Package: randy
Type: Package
Title: Data and Functions for Modelling Goals Scored in Premier League Football Matches
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Daf Howells
Maintainer: Daf Howells <dafhowells@yahoo.co.uk>
Description: This package provides historical premier league football match data for the purpose of modelling goal outcomes.
      The data sets provide running averages for goals scored and conceded by a team in the same fixture historically.
      Also included are running xG averages.    
